但送貨時間勁慢，D地點又唔係周圍有，垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁啱我嗰頭得4px <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前一直用都冇事<br />\n今次奶撻 永不錄用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後搭車俾貴啲都好都用順豐算"},{"pid":"08af6ce4d6b8ae65ac1b8a8f09d9256dff865889","tid":518970,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪唔見左件貨啦？ 搵taobao介入啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱打左去 淘寶話預三個工作天發貨<br />\n都係得個預字<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b77f29d17cb3f0b0a9a3a6098b2dc0ce1c501c2","tid":518970,"uid":97451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:09:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff804bb8464c284e1b2ff32c8893b623a849a724","tid":518970,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n21號話派件不成功<br />\n我屌佢老母啦果日一個電話都冇收到過<br />\n我就唔信佢寧願攞返件所謂大貨走都唔撚諗辦法送走件貨<br />\n之後問客服又話要2個工作天<br />\n仆佢個街10個工作天都嚟緊仲係咩消息都冇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">永不錄用4PX呀屌你老母垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇得點樣告佢架？<br />\n官網連最遲幾多個月內收到都冇寫 好大個bug<br />\n一味用未能保證時效黎拖真係吹唔鳩佢漲<br />\n件貨係佢度真係任佢宰割<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b81ca0b439d565dae8409208981803b20746cf","tid":518970,"uid":89740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"呢間野真係仆街黎 我件野雙11買 到而家都未有 但一路話係大強倉 都唔知點搞"},{"pid":"1455fea33b488d3bc933d63826c87e3be9a35391","tid":518970,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來宜家4px搞到咁，好似仲愈黎愈少自提點，仲衰過中通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:之前一直幫襯開4px,但宜家轉左非官方集運</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇好介紹 我成日都怕非官方會有風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e10d3b84fc5ae2512da101953f38b0b20a2624d","tid":518970,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:13:19.000Z","msg":"一個order，4件貨，分4次送黎<br />\n<br />\n真係冇咁多時間招呼佢"},{"pid":"d629cfdd56dd4b6a875105c1732393968af342e7","tid":518970,"uid":20379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"我試過一對鞋佢送左4日，我屌足佢咁多日"},{"pid":"b4099265e58a75a97f94ea9eebbffd52abac5850","tid":518970,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:15:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順豐都係咁 連續幾次 明明只係買耳環同啲環保袋 夠膽死話貨品太大 一係就話智能櫃無哂位 要等8至10個工作天</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母我細件都唔俾我揀自提<br />\nHold撚住件貨又唔肯派<br />\n我去拎晨早拎完洗埋着殘埋添喇"},{"pid":"b8e414b6203163f2f012644403676c916beb25f8","tid":518970,"uid":50491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:16:43.000Z","msg":"雙11苦主<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d017d8cf6b61bde6cb2c3639ecac5521095d3463","tid":518970,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:17:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你可以喺客服同佢退款<br />\n會包埋件貨既價錢<br />\n我雙11買野 佢雙12都無寄黎<br />\n我話總之我貨都唔要 你地退款<br />\n後尾成功退到 但係退落支付寶 唔係via淘寶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係焗你再幫佢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6870fc00fdb5afb08bef3b069376211d3c20e9ec","tid":518970,"uid":72469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T11:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我雙十一買左個不銹鋼架到而家都未送貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解唔追追佢？"},{"pid":"907e8fb5e96beceaf540d263b58d52d217af613a","tid":518970,"uid":146299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1455fea33